data.title: Princess Pauline of Württemberg (1810–1856)
data.meta_description: Princess Pauline Friederike Marie was Duchess consort of Nassau from 1829 to 1839 as the second wife of William, Duke of Nassau. She was a member of the House of Württemberg and a princess of Württemberg by birth.
